WYSIWYM.transformer
Class AutomaticGenerator

java.lang.Object
  WYSIWYM.transformer.AutomaticGenerator

public class AutomaticGenerator
extends Object

AutomaticGenerator adds automatically generated information to the semantic graph, such as the date of deposit and the depositor details. It also reads information from the Sesame archive about the user or objects the user has requested information about through browsing options, and adds it to the Graph. Finally it also retrieves information about search results and put it in QueryResultGraphs.

Version:
1.1 27-02-2007, 1.2 27-02-2008
Author:
Feikje Hielkema
